original_title: 美少女み～つけた。 田舎のお嬢様女子大生が3年間片想いのあの人を忘れたくてAVデビュー 弥生みづき
overview: A young female college student who grew up in the countryside and just moved to Tokyo in the spring to go on to school makes her AV debut! Appearing in an AV, she wants to forget about her unrequited love for three years... I don't think it's an AV, but contrary to her warm appearance, she has a firm will and does everything with her pleasant SEX. I want you to forget The first time she took her clothes off, and her first SEX in public. Why is this girl in AV? ? A work by Hajimete, a beautiful girl with a dignified appearance that makes you think.
title: Honey Hunter: A Countryside College Princess Turns To Porn To Forget The One Who Got Away Starring Mizuki Yayoi
